rComments: A phenomenal prof that made everything from fish to lizards interesting. Would 100% recommend his Vertebrate Diversity course. Easy exams if you study. He gives you a lot of the questions in advance.

Really wants you to succeed in his class and provides everything you need to do it. Highly approachable and, like someone said already, gives good clear lectures with emphasis on important points you need to know for the test.
EEB266 Invert Diversity. Very Clear in lectures. Reiterates important points. Tests  are easy compared to the difficulty of the material. Funny and very approachable
He's a great professor who goes above and beyond, and clearly has a passion for the subject.
